Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:50.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:53.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:58.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,暗闇に浮かんだ　棚引く淡い光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:03.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,まだ見ぬ未知の陽は　誰を照らし出すの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:08.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,愛しき My Buddy　哀しみくれても Don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:13.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,何があっても　生き抜け That's all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:15.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…　さぁ手を伸ばせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.83,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…　この闇を抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:20.04,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…　脈打つ鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:23.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger　飛び出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,見つめる世界の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:34.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,小さな胸に　憧れを　詰め込んだら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:44.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,琥珀の夢　約束のあの場所まで　いざ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:51.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,キミを想う気持ちは　この空よりもでかい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:57.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,無限大　いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:03:04.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:08.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Comment: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:50.17,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:53.09,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:58.22,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,黯淡的光晕  浮现于黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:03.44,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,未见未知的阳光  会将谁照亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:08.19,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的伙伴  就算沉浸于悲伤也不慌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:13.15,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么  活下去才是唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:15.45,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…  来伸出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.83,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…  穿过这片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:20.04,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…  冲击全身的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:23.66,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger  起飞吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.34,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,紧盯着世界的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:34.18,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,当小小胸膛填满了憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:44.10,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,琥珀之梦  朝着约定的地点出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:51.48,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,对你的关心关爱  比这天空更宽广
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:57.62,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,无限扩张  永无止境
Comment: 0,0:02:57.62,0:03:04.54,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:08.42,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
